playstore_details.title: PinGo Auth
playstore_details.description:
PinGo Auth generates Time based One Time Password (OTP) for authentication.

PinGo Auth OTP Verification provides stronger security for your account by requiring a second step of verification when you sign in.

Features:
* Works Offline - Generate verification OTP without data or wifi connection.
* Biometrics support - You can login using your Biometric credentials if your device has Biometric configuration.
* Dark theme support - App automatically adjusts the Day/Night theme based on your device's theme selection.

Required Permissions:
- Camera: This app needs permission to access your camera to scan the QR code to inject your code in the app.
playstore_details.summary: PinGo Authentication App generates 2-Step Verification codes on your phone.
playstore_details.summaryHTML: PinGo Authentication App generates 2-Step Verification codes on your phone.
